               MAX-ACCESS  read-create
               STATUS      current
               DESCRIPTION
                   "DMAC Type.
                    default: 0,
                    0: Any - Don't care.
                    1: Multicast - Frame must be multicast.
                    2: Broadcast - Frame must be broadcast.
