                    the switch receives a success indication.Indicates that
                    the supplicant has successfully authenticated to
                    the backend server.
                    -1: no support."
               ::= {     sispm10403166lNASPortCounterEntry 14 }

    sispm10403166lNASPortReceiveBackendServerAuthFailures OBJECT-TYPE
               SYNTAX      Integer32(-1..1000000)
               MAX-ACCESS  read-only
               STATUS      current
               DESCRIPTION
                   "802.1X- and MAC-based:Counts the number of times that the
                    switch receives a failure message.This indicates that the
                    supplicant has not authenticated to the backend
                    server.
                    -1: no support."
               ::= {     sispm10403166lNASPortCounterEntry 15 }

    sispm10403166lNASPortTransmitBackendServerResponses OBJECT-TYPE
               SYNTAX      Integer32(-1..1000000)
               MAX-ACCESS  read-only
               STATUS      current
               DESCRIPTION
